text.tspan: Share of consumer expenditure spent on food vs. GDP per capita, 2015
Share of per capita consumer expenditure spent on food (in the year 2015) versus gross domestic product (GDP) per
capita, measured in US$. 'Food' in this case excludes alcoholic beverages and tobacco products. Food expenditure
relates only to food bought for consumption at home (i.e. it excludes out-of-home food purchases).
